Honors[edit]
His native Northside neighborhood of Pittsburgh renamed a major highway leading to Heinz Field in his honor.[38]
On July 26, 2011, Hayden was inducted into the Air Force Reserve Officer Training Corps Distinguished Alumni in a ceremony at Maxwell AFB, Alabama, officiated by Lt. Gen. Allen G. Peck, Commander, Air University.[12]
